Updated the shared markdown hover link rule in `website/src/css/custom.css`.

Hovered and focus-visible markdown links now explicitly use the Transit red accent instead of inheriting the blue hover path:
- hover text color is `var(--transit-route-red-strong)`
- hover underline color is `rgba(143, 24, 34, 0.32)`

This removes the remaining blue hover underline/accent in docs content.
